  "body": "The original docs stated that forceUpdate() will trigger the render methods of child components, but that's not exactly true. Child components will check their `shouldComponentUpdate()` first so `render()` will only be triggered conditionally on children. It's also more clear to explicitly mention that `shouldComponentUpdate()` will be skipped in the component where `forceUpdate()` is called.\n",
